      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### app/core/database.py\n\n\nengine = create_engine(settings.DATABASE_URL, ...)\nвҶ“\nSessionLocal = sessionmaker(bind=engine, ...)\nвҶ“\n(database object generator)\n```python\ndef get_db():\n\tdb = SessionLocal()\t\n\ttry:\n\t\tyield db\n\tfinally:\n\t\tdb.close()\n```\n\n\\+ Base",
